text: Kemnath () is a small town in Tirschenreuth, in Bavaria, Germany. It is near the Fichtelgebirge, 24 km southeast of Bayreuth. The town's motto is "das Tor zur Oberpfalz," which translates into English as "The Door to the Upper Palatinate." ==References== ==Other websites== * Official homepage of the town of Kemnath (In German) Category:Tirschenreuth (district)
